# Core Thesis

## Purpose

This section defines the central argument of the project.

## Draft thesis

Enterprise AI systems may become more durable when they support control, interpretation, escalation discipline, and accountability rather than simply adding broader interfaces or more visible automation.

The strongest opportunity may not always sit in the broadest system. It may sit in bounded layers that help organizations determine what deserves attention, why it deserves attention, and how human accountability is preserved.

